# obj_dir*/ / build_*_tb/ globs above don't catch.
obj_iso*/
w2*/
tb_iso*/
tb_a850/
tb_p1/

# Root-level run/done markers + EDA scratch from the fit/INT3 campaign
*.flag
*_err.txt
*.bin
bak_lint.txt
cur_lint.txt
scratch/

# Underscore-prefixed scratch scripts (private one-offs; the convention
